title: Kaley Cuoco slams dating rumours with ex Johnny Galecki
text:
Washington: If you were thinking that Kaley Cuoco had something going on with her former boyfriend Johnny Galecki then it"s time to pop the bubble.
Previously, reports circulated that the 29-year-old actress' marriage to Ryan Sweeting suffered because she never got over her love for her 'Big Bang Theory' co-star, reports E! Online.
 
  A photo posted by @normancook onOct 14, 2015 at 10:56am PDT
However, Kaley Cuoco took to Instagram and posted a picture of herself and Galecki, captioning it, "So sorry to disappoint, but no home wreckers or secret flings going on here Me and @sanctionedjohnnygalecki are just the best of buds- Leonard and Penny will just have to suffice!!"
